Comment.val: /*fetches the instrument details and trading times*/

ExpSyntax.val: Trim({0,1006633013}) &' inner join koerskodes B on A.BE_VOLGNUMMER=B.KC_BE_VOLGNUMMER'

Text.val: Because more than one instrument can be requested, reset virtuals
No search criteria for instrument found in request
Instrument is written as parameter of the errorresponse

SQL_STMT_U.val: select * from ( select A.BE_SYMBOOL,A.BE_OPTIETYPE,A.BE_EXPIRATIEDATUM, A.BE_EXERCISEPRIJS,A.BE_CODE,A.BE_OMS_1, A.BE_BI_NUMMER,A.BE_BR_NUMMER,A.BE_MUNTSOORT, A.BE_NOMINAAL,A.BE_PRIJS_FACTOR,A.BE_BV_BEURS, A.BE_INTEREST_TYPE,A.BE_HANDELEN_TOEGESTAAN, A.BE_BGS_FONDS,A.BE_VERWERKINGSTIJD,A.BE_VOLGNUMMER, A.BE_GENOTEERD_IN_PERC,A.BE_TIME_HORIZON_CODE, A.BE_TIME_HORIZON_YEARS,A.BE_URL_FUND_INFO, A.BE_GEBLOKKEERD FROM :1 WHERE :2 and A.BE_OPTIETYPE in (' ', 'CALL', 'PUT', 'FUT') order by A.BE_SYMBOOL,A.BE_OPTIETYPE,A.BE_EXPIRATIEDATUM,A.BE_EXERCISEPRIJS) where rownum <=~3

Text.val: When no record was found, this is reported in a Warning-response
